text: Carterica mucronata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Olivier in 1795. It is known from Bolivia, Brazil, French Guiana and Peru.BioLib.cz - Carterica mucronata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1795
